[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]There is a particular need for clarity over arrangements and support for claimants transitioning from supported to independent acc
[normal]ommodation. There is a risk that claimants could move from living in supported accommodation where there housing costs are paid directly to their landlord
[normal],
[normal] to living 
