[normal]means that people are now expected to pay a significant proportion of their income on council tax.
[normal]9.2.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]St Mungo’s runs Peer Advice Link, a resettlement and tenancy support programme st
[normal]affed by volunteers. One of our volunteers now has to pay £13 a month in council tax. His income consists of £56.80 a week Jobseekers Allowance.
[normal] He therefore has to spend over five per cent of his income on council tax.
